  <evidence rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">COOKIES AND SIMILAR TECHNOLOGIES Yahoo may set and access Yahoo cookies on your computer We may also set and access device identifiers which could include IP address user agent information browser version OS type and version and device provided identifiers Once you log into Yahoo on your device Yahoo may recognize your device to provide you with a personalized experience independent of your device settings You can control your personalized experience across Yahoo through our Ad Interest Manager Learn more</evidence>
